<html>

<body>
    <pre>
Hello <%= client_name %>,<br>
Greetings from FarziEngineer!<br>
There has been decrement in sales for <b>HRS <%= start_time %> - <%= end_time %></b> in comparison to average sales of last 3 days in the same hour.<br>
Hourly Average Order of last three days: <b><%= average_order %></b> and for today is <b><%= today_total_order %></b>.<br>
Here you can find more detail and see if any action require.<br>
<table style="border:1px solid black;text-align:left;">
    <tr>
        <th style="border:1px solid black;text-align:center;">Date</th>
        <th style="border:1px solid black;text-align:center;">Hour</th>
        <th style="border:1px solid black;text-align:center;">Order Count</th>
        <th style="border:1px solid black;text-align:center;">Order Value</th>
    </tr>
    <% orders.forEach(order => { %>
        <tr>
            <td style="border:1px solid black;text-align:center;"><%= order.date %></td>
            <td style="border:1px solid black;text-align:center;"><%= order.hour %></td>
            <td style="border:1px solid black;text-align:center;"><%= order.order_count %></td>
            <td style="border:1px solid black;text-align:center;">Rs. <%= order.total_net_amount %></td>
        </tr>
    <% }) %>
        
</table>
<br><br>
Sincerely,
Farziengineer Team
<br>
<b>Note:</b> This email is automatically generated, please do not reply. Any action to be taken further on this information required manual intervention. There is no action to be performed automatically basis of this email.
</pre>
</body>

</html>